<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Nikolaus I. von Lobkowitz-Hassenstein, oberster Schreiber der Landtafeln von Böhmen und Hauptmann des Landfriedens zu Saaz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache bei Heinrich von Kaufungen, Hauptmann zu Totzau, wegen Freilassung des Wilhelm von Castell, Herausgabe seiner Habe und Ledigsagen der Bürgen, da er nicht Bürger zu Meißen sondern zu Nürnberg ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_216" id="107r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_216_r2l16">Dem Erſamen fürnemen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Nycolae von 
<del rend="strikethrough"> k </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l17">lobkovvicʒ <expan>Oberſte<ex>n</ex></expan> Schreyber der lantTafeln des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l18">künigreichs cʒu Beheym vnd hauptman des lantfrids </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l19">cʒacʒer kreiſes etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_216_r2l20">Erſamer vnd lıeber her hauptman . vns ıſt fürbraht <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l21">vvie der Erber vnd veſte <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> hauptman cʒu dacʒaw </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l22">den <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Caſtell des Steffans von Caſtel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> ſun . für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l23"><expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> Meiſſner daʒ Er in Meıſſen güter lıgend habe vnd da </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l24">ſedelhaft ſein ſüll . gefangen hab / Darauff vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l25">cʒu <expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> tun . daʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Caſtel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>reht<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ynvvonend<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l26"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ıſt / vnd vns cʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſtet vnd <expan>nymand<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Als vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l28">das <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_216_r2l27">ſelber </ab></add> cʒu guter maſʒ an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>briefe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l29">
<add><ab facs="#facs_216_r1l1">auch </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd cʒuvviſſen getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Hyrumb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l30"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige hılff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l31">vnd <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ von <expan>kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweiſen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l32">daʒ derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd auch ſein <expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan> die Er von <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_216_r2l33">venknüſſe wegen geſecʒt hat als wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ledig </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_217" id="107v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l1">vnd ob <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ıht <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> wer worden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l2">wıder <expan>vverd<ex>en</ex></expan> / Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l3">Das <expan>vvolle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> fürnemkeit <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r1l4"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıııȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı.</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_216" id="107r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem ersamen, fürnemen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Nycolae von Lobkowicz,
                                <expan>oberste<ex>n</ex></expan> schreyber der lanttafeln des
                        künigreichs czu Beheym und hauptman des lantfrids Czaczer kreises etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber her hauptman, uns ist fürbraht
                            <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie der erber und veste
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, hauptman czu Daczaw, den
                                <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Castell, des Steffans von Castel
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> sun, für <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Meissner, daz er in Meissen güter ligend habe und da sedelhaft sein süll,
                        gefangen hab. Darauff wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> czu <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> tun,
                        daz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Castel <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>reht<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ynwonend<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ist und uns czu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> stet und
                                <expan>nymand<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> als wir, das <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add>selber</add> czu guter masz an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>briefe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>auch</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und czuwissen getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Hyrumb
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff
                        und <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von <expan>Kauffu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        beweisen wöllet, daz derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und auch sein <expan>pürge<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        die er von <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> venknüsse wegen geseczt hat,
                        als wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, ledig, <pb facs="#facs_217" id="107v"/>und ob
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> iht <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> wer
                        worden, wider <expan>werd<ex>en</ex></expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        fürnemkeit <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome
                                <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
